<dl id="n11055c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n11" href="#n11055c">N11 (VI.B.5)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n11all.htm#n11055c"> 55(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> when Mr J&mdash; was / blind drunk</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[Account of poisoning at the Blue Anchor Hotel of Mr Jones by Mr Vaquier]</font> <font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> I can say that if ever so cowardly and criminal an idea had been borne in my brain it would have been much easier for me to rid myself of Mr. Jones in the evening when no one was present and <mark>when Mr. Jones was blind drunk</mark>. <small> <a name="DM27may24" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#DM27may24"><cite title="source">Daily Mail</cite></a> (27 May 1924) 10/1-2</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
